"annotation, selecting it. The default callout displays the annotation’s title","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and subtitle. You can add accessory views to either end of the callout by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementing the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:leftCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" methods. You can further","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"customize the callout’s contents by implementing the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the return value is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", or if this method is absent from the delegate, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"if the annotation lacks a title, the annotation will not show a callout even","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when selected.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related examples","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to show callouts for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotationCanShowCallout:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Map